metadata.name: #01 - Bobby
metadata.description:
Have you ever heard of a skeleton walking around in the cemetery rather than going to sleep?

Have you ever caught a glimpse of her sparkling eyes or seen her terrifying teeth?

Bobby, the skeleton who fears going to sleep at night, is here!

Bobby is the first piece of the unique 50-piece Skeleton Friends collection.

2048x2048px
30 fps (animated in twos)
352 frames, 10sec, Loop
